Nutrient data for: PHILADELPHIA CREAM CHEESE-SOFT SALMON, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210307422

Ingredients: Medium fat soft CHEESE, water, smoked SALMON 4.5% (SALMON, salt, smoke), onion, salt, modified starch, stabilisers (locust bean gum, carrageenan), garlic, acids (lactic acid, citric acid), flavourings (contain FISH), emulsifier (mono- and diglycerides of fatty acids), dill, white pepper, lemon juice concentrate, smoke.
